§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Given a vector $x ∈ 𝗥^n$ and a subspace $S ⊂ 𝗥^n$, what
    is the closest point in $S$ to $x$. ⦉
⦉

§ Result ⦉
<statement type='proposition'>
  ‖ Suppose $U ∈ 𝗥^{n × k}$ with $U^⊤U = I$. ⦉

  ‖ Then
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \textstyle ⦉

      ‖ \proj_{U}(x) = UU^⊤x ⦉
    ⦉⦉
</statement>
